Detailed Description

template<typename T>
class roboptim::retargeting::MinimumJerkTrajectory< T >

Minimum jerk trajectory computation.

The curve is parametrized by a vector of four parameters:

  • position start
  • position end
  • velocity start
  • acceleration start

This class is a partial implementation of a Trajectory. Some methods will return a runtime_error if called.
